{"type":"app","meta":{"headers":{"x-nextjs-stale-time":"300","x-nextjs-prerender":"1","x-next-cache-tags":"_N_T_/layout,_N_T_/terms/layout,_N_T_/terms/page,_N_T_/terms"},"segmentPaths":["/_tree","/_full","/terms/__PAGE__","/terms","/_index","/_head"]},"html":"<!DOCTYPE html><!--k_w22G2V8NmVohKjMTgoo--><html lang=\"en\"><head><meta charSet=\"utf-8\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/_next/static/media/797e433ab948586e-s.p.dbea232f.woff2\" as=\"font\" crossorigin=\"\" type=\"font/woff2\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/_next/static/media/caa3a2e1cccd8315-s.p.853070df.woff2\" as=\"font\" crossorigin=\"\" type=\"font/woff2\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"image\" imageSrcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Flensically-logo-white-with-black-bg.png&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Flensically-logo-white-with-black-bg.png&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 2x\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/dd0b32f5ab39efa9.css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"script\" fetchPriority=\"low\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/bb8f42ac442d7a63.js\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/82abf2d65f5428ae.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/aee6c7720838f8a2.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/3b2ed5fb7ad1f280.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/turbopack-8fa6a74498c6fa50.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/8cd5fe156f301608.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/ff1a16fafef87110.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/d2be314c3ece3fbe.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/b4872826d9ffb447.js\" async=\"\"></script><meta name=\"next-size-adjust\" content=\"\"/><title>Terms of Service | Lensically</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"Basic terms governing access to and use of the Lensically application.\"/><link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https://lensically.com/terms\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico?favicon.0b3bf435.ico\" sizes=\"256x256\" type=\"image/x-icon\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/a6dad97d9634a72d.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"geist_a71539c9-module__T19VSG__variable geist_mono_8d43a2aa-module__8Li5zG__variable antialiased\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><div class=\"min-h-screen bg-white text-black\"><main class=\"mx-auto flex w-full max-w-4xl flex-col gap-8 px-6 py-16 sm:px-8\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" href=\"/\"><img alt=\"Lensically logo\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"h-16 w-16 rounded-md\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Flensically-logo-white-with-black-bg.png&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Flensically-logo-white-with-black-bg.png&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Flensically-logo-white-with-black-bg.png&amp;w=128&amp;q=75\"/><span class=\"text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight\">Lensically</span></a><div class=\"space-y-3\"><p class=\"text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-slate-500\">Public Terms Of Service</p><h1 class=\"text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900\">Terms of service</h1><p class=\"max-w-3xl text-base leading-7 text-slate-600\">These terms describe the basic rules for accessing and using Lensically. By using the application, you agree to follow these terms and any applicable provider platform requirements connected to your use of the service.</p></div><section class=\"rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900\">Official public review URL</h2><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600\">The canonical public terms page for reviewer access is available at<!-- --> <a class=\"font-medium text-slate-900 underline\" href=\"https://lensically.com/terms\">https://lensically.com/terms</a>.</p></section><section class=\"rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-6\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900\">Using Lensically</h2><ul class=\"mt-4 list-disc space-y-3 pl-5 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-700\"><li>Use the application only for lawful purposes and only with accounts and data you are authorized to access.</li><li>Do not attempt to bypass authentication, access controls, rate limits, or provider restrictions.</li><li>Do not interfere with the service, abuse platform features, or use Lensically to violate third-party terms.</li></ul></section><section class=\"rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900\">Accounts and connected services</h2><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600\">Some Lensically features require an authenticated account and a connected Threads account or supported OAuth sign-in provider. You are responsible for maintaining the accuracy of your account information and for using connected services in compliance with the applicable provider terms.</p></section><section class=\"rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900\">Account deletion and access</h2><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600\">Lensically provides self-serve account deletion from the authenticated account settings area. When an account is permanently deleted, associated application records tied to that user are removed from the system according to the product’s implemented deletion flow.</p><p class=\"mt-4 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600\">Privacy practices are described at<!-- --> <a class=\"font-medium text-slate-900 underline\" href=\"/privacy\">https://lensically.com/privacy</a>, and public deletion instructions are available at<!-- --> <a class=\"font-medium text-slate-900 underline\" href=\"/data-deletion\">https://lensically.com/data-deletion</a>.</p></section><section class=\"rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900\">Contact</h2><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600\">If you have questions about these terms or need support related to your use of the service, contact<!-- --> <a class=\"font-medium text-slate-900 underline\" href=\"mailto:support@lensically.com\">support@lensically.com</a>.</p></section></main></div><!--$--><!--/$--><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/bb8f42ac442d7a63.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[83917,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/8cd5fe156f301608.js\\\"],\\\"AuthProvider\\\"]\\n3:I[39756,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/ff1a16fafef87110.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/d2be314c3ece3fbe.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n4:I[37457,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/ff1a16fafef87110.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/d2be314c3ece3fbe.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n5:I[22016,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/8cd5fe156f301608.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/b4872826d9ffb447.js\\\"],\\\"\\\"]\\n6:I[5500,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/8cd5fe156f301608.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/b4872826d9ffb447.js\\\"],\\\"Image\\\"]\\nf:I[68027,[],\\\"default\\\"]\\n:HL[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/dd0b32f5ab39efa9.css\\\",\\\"style\\\"]\\n:HL[\\\"/_next/static/media/797e433ab948586e-s.p.dbea232f.woff2\\\",\\\"font\\\",{\\\"crossOrigin\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"font/woff2\\\"}]\\n:HL[\\\"/_next/static/media/caa3a2e1cccd8315-s.p.853070df.woff2\\\",\\\"font\\\",{\\\"crossOrigin\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"font/woff2\\\"}]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"0:{\\\"P\\\":null,\\\"b\\\":\\\"k_w22G2V8NmVohKjMTgoo\\\",\\\"c\\\":[\\\"\\\",\\\"terms\\\"],\\\"q\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"i\\\":false,\\\"f\\\":[[[\\\"\\\",{\\\"children\\\":[\\\"terms\\\",{\\\"children\\\":[\\\"__PAGE__\\\",{}]}]},\\\"$undefined\\\",\\\"$undefined\\\",true],[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$1\\\",\\\"c\\\",{\\\"children\\\":[[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"link\\\",\\\"0\\\",{\\\"rel\\\":\\\"stylesheet\\\",\\\"href\\\"